WEBVTT

1
00:45:16.787 --> 00:45:18.584 
这张画我看了很不开心
Makes me unhappy.

2
00:45:20.891 --> 00:45:23.485 
这样的话，那就不看了
In that case, you just put it aside.

3
00:45:25.563 --> 00:45:27.622 
看，帆布
Look, study the canvas.

4
00:45:28.766 --> 00:45:31.496 
- 帆布？ - 为你的肖像准备的帆布
- Canvas? - Canvas for your portrait.

5
00:45:31.936 --> 00:45:34.530 
你的肖像，这是我们早就约好了的
Your portrait. One we planned.

6
00:45:35.740 --> 00:45:37.799 
埃本，你真的要帮我画？
Eben, if you wanted to.

7
00:45:37.875 --> 00:45:41.641 
我总相信总有一天你会来的，我一直都在等这一天，坐到那里去
I was so sure you will be here one day. I haven't been able to do anything else. Sit over here.

8
00:45:41.712 --> 00:45:43.236 
- 坐那里吗？ - 对
- Here? - Oh yes.

9
00:45:43.314 --> 00:45:45.282 
就是那里，我一直都期待你坐的地方
Right there, where I've dreamed you'll sit.

10
00:45:45.349 --> 00:45:48.011 
- 那些女孩一定嫉妒的发疯 - 把头偏一点
- Les will be so jealous. When I tell him. - Turn here the other way.

